33namespace WebCore {
34
35class KeepaliveRequestTracker final : public CachedRawResourceClient {
36public:
37 ~KeepaliveRequestTracker();
38 bool tryRegisterRequest(CachedResource&);
39
40 // CachedRawResourceClient.
41 void responseReceived(CachedResource&, const ResourceResponse&, CompletionHandler<void()>&&) final;
42 void notifyFinished(CachedResource&, const NetworkLoadMetrics&) final;
43
44private:
45 void registerRequest(CachedResource&);
46 void unregisterRequest(CachedResource&);
47
48 Vector<CachedResourceHandle<CachedResource>> m_inflightKeepaliveRequests;
49 uint64_t m_inflightKeepaliveBytes { 0 };
50};
